data.description: The Elgin Plan by by D.R. Horton Homes! This Gorgeous 1 Story Home features Luxurious Vinyl Floors Throughout and Carpeting in Bedrooms! Amazing Gourmet Kitchen w/Gorgeous Granite Counters, Stainless Steel Appliances, Working & Eat-in Island with Stainless Steel Sink, Tall Cabinets will surround you & flows gracefully into your Casual Dining Area & Amazing Family Room with direct access to your Covered Patio & Backyard! Primary Suite w/High Ceilings tucked away for privacy & Luxurious Bath with Dual Private Sink Vanity, Massive Shower(Room for 2!) & Huge Walk In Closet! 3 Secondary Bedrooms and 1 Full Bath! Amazing Standard Energy Features include: HERS Energy Rated, Tank-less Gas Water Heater & The Smart Home Automation: Smart Thermostat, Electronic Deadbolt, Skybell Doorbell, Smart Lighting & Amazon Eco Dot & more! Amenity Center w/Pool, Lap Pool, Water Slides, Pavilion, Playground, Soccer Fields & more!
